<div id="pf4458" class="pf w4e h303" data-page-no="4458"><div class="pc pc4458 w4e h303"><div class="t m1adc xb9 h5 y2d6b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 6 August 5-11 </div><div class="t m883 x27 h5 y88f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Hurt not the earth, neither the sea, </div><div class="t mb66 xb9 h5 y2069 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">nor the trees, till we have sealed the </div><div class="t mb85 x3 h5 y137a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">servants of our God in their </div><div class="t m15d x3 h5 y71b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">foreheads&quot; (Rev. 7:3). </div><div class="t m6bd x27 h35 y20e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Both the Bible and the spirit of </div><div class="t m146 x3 h35 y20e4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prophecy speak about the sealing of </div><div class="t me12 x3 h35 y13cd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the children of God. What is the </div><div class="t m6af x3 h35 y9d8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sealing? It is a spiritual process of </div><div class="t m232 x3 h35 y1268 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sanctification, invisible to the human </div><div class="t ma74 x3 h35 y15ec ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">eyes. It is a personal as well as a </div><div class="t m344 x3 h35 y540 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cooperative work. The sealing begins </div><div class="t m2ee x3 h35 ya12 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the day of an individual&apos;s conversion </div><div class="t m9b7 x3 h35 ya04 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and ends at the close of his probation. </div><div class="t m2a2 x3 h35 y85d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This could be at his death or at the end </div><div class="t ma93 x3 h35 yf88 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the investigative judgment. </div><div class="t m1b5 x11 h35 y8a4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This work of sealing is done by God, </div><div class="t m202 x3 h35 y13cf ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">by the Holy Spirit, and by the angels. It </div><div class="t m221 x3 h35 y302 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">consists of writing the principles of the </div><div class="t m3ec x3 h35 y79a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">divine law—including the fourth </div><div class="t m2df x3 h35 yf ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">commandment—on the tables of flesh </div><div class="t m7ae x3 h35 y510 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in the heart. In other words, the effect </div><div class="t m1a4 x3 h35 y37d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the sealing will be the </div><div class="t m119 x3 h35 y19cf ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">transformation of the individual life so </div><div class="t m222 x3 h35 y572 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that it represents the perfect character </div><div class="t ma97 x3 h35 y476 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of Christ. </div><div class="t m2d3 x11 h35 y2e9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The process of sealing is going on </div><div class="t m8f2 xbd h35 y9f6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">right now and will end at the </div><div class="t m530 xbd h35 y66d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">beginning of the time of trouble, that </div><div class="t m2e1 xbd h35 ydc4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is to say, at the end of probationary </div><div class="t m9b5 xbd h35 y801 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">time for the human race. </div><div class="t m88b x11 h35 y307 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The sealing achieves at least four </div><div class="t m2a7 xbd h35 y52e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">important objectives: </div><div class="t m7df x11 h35 y359 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. It establishes in the life of the </div><div class="t m3aa xbd h35 yafd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">saints the great principles of the </div><div class="t m3e8 xbd h35 y9a7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">perfect law of God so that they will not </div><div class="t m98 xbd h35 yfbd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">be broken after the close of probation. </div><div class="t m7d6 x56 h35 y88f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m74b x7b h35 y88f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Amidst apostasy and fierce </div><div class="t m4b6 x5a h35 y2069 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">persecution it causes those who </div><div class="t m786 x5a h35 y4fa ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">receive it to be absolutely faithful in </div><div class="t m80e x5a h35 ybec ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sabbath observance as a testimony of </div><div class="t m113 x1c h35 y7ec ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">their loyalty to God. </div><div class="t m210 x56 h35 y1010 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m81f x7b h35 y1010 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">It prepares the faithful to go </div><div class="t mbbc x5a h35 yaaa ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">through the time of trouble—a time </div><div class="t mfab x5a h35 ye62 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">without a mediator—without falling </div><div class="t mb1a x5a h35 y8ff ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">into sin, and thus remaining </div><div class="t m7b5 x5a h35 y39e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">unharmed. </div><div class="t ma7c x56 h35 ya73 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m12b x7b h35 ya73 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">It preserves the faithful from the </div><div class="t m363 x5a h35 y2dc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">plagues and from final destruction. </div><div class="t m14a x5a h5 ya04 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m23f x5a h5 y7b0 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m156 x86 h5 y7b0 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Till we have sealed&quot; </div><div class="t m635 x86 h5 y666 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 7:1-4) </div><div class="t m558 x5a h5 yf7d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m13e x86 h5 yf7d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What the Seal Is </div><div class="t mce x86 h5 yef7 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rom. 4:11) </div><div class="t mb7 x5a h5 y8bc ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m7b7 x86 h5 y8bc ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Time of Sealing </div><div class="t m751 x86 h5 y525 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(2 Cor. 1:21, 22) </div><div class="t m1ce x5a h5 y120d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m442 x86 h5 y120d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sanctification and Preparation </div><div class="t m307 x4b h5 y907 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Eph. 4:30) </div><div class="t m8a8 x5a h5 y3a8 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t ma71 x86 h5 y76f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Conditions for the Sealing </div><div class="t mf7 x86 h5 ya79 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 7:4) </div><div class="t m2ef x5a h5 y40a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m34c x86 h5 ybd9 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Fulfilling the Conditions </div><div class="t m107e x4b h5 y11d0 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Eph. 1:13) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
